00:28:14,267 --> 00:28:16,634
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

439
00:28:59,567 --> 00:29:00,768
Martine.

440
00:29:01,868 --> 00:29:03,267
Martine.

441
00:29:06,701 --> 00:29:08,734
[HEART BEATING STEADILY]

442
00:29:17,234 --> 00:29:18,434
[WHISPERS]
Oh, my God.

443
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:40,801
[VOMITS]

444
00:29:43,567 --> 00:29:44,834
[GROANS]

445
00:29:44,967 --> 00:29:46,601
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

446
00:29:46,734 --> 00:29:49,033
- [FEEDBACK OVER RADIO]
- Mayday, mayday, mayday.

447
00:29:49,167 --> 00:29:52,234
