00:33:21,601 --> 00:33:23,134
[GRUNTING]

501
00:33:45,000 --> 00:33:46,801
[GULPING]

502
00:33:57,167 --> 00:33:58,501
[HISSES]

503
00:34:06,033 --> 00:34:08,067
[BEEPS]

504
00:34:12,033 --> 00:34:13,501
[RECORDER BEEPS]

505
00:34:14,567 --> 00:34:16,200
As a result of my procedure,

506
00:34:16,334 --> 00:34:19,234
<i>I have an overpowering urge
to consume...</i>

507
00:34:21,567 --> 00:34:23,067
<i>blood.</i>

508
00:34:23,200 --> 00:34:24,634
Human blood.

